---
description: Rules for discussion threads, comments, votes, and community notifications.
globs:
  - client/src/components/discussion/**
  - client/src/lib/communityClient.ts
  - supabase/community_migration.sql
  - client/src/pages/Home.tsx
---

- Use authenticated writes for comments/votes/notifications; reads can remain public where intended.
- Keep thread scope deterministic (`scope_type` + `scope_key`) for game and edition contexts.
- Favor optimistic but reversible UX: refresh after writes and handle permission failures gracefully.
- Enforce one vote per user per comment via unique constraints + upsert patterns.
- Keep discussion mobile-friendly and accessible with clear action labels.
- Include “hot take” surfacing from objective score signals (vote totals).
